      • getCredentials

        public Credentials getCredentials()
        Gets the credentials. The credentials for the binding. Additional key-value pairs are passed through from the resource brokers. After a credential is created for a service, it can be viewed at any time for users that need the API key value. However, all users must have the correct level of access to see the details of a credential that includes the API key value. For additional details, see [viewing a credential](https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/account?topic=account-service_credentials&interface=ui#viewing-credentials-ui) or the service’s documentation.
        Returns:
        the credentials
